# Project Architecture: ChargeMOD Support AI Agent

This document outlines the architecture, components, and data/control flows of the ChargeMOD Support AI Agent. The agent is built on top of Flask and leverages a multi-LLM orchestration pipeline to perform troubleshooting, charger diagnostics, action control (remote start/stop/booking), customer lookups, estimations, and RAG-based query resolution.

